comments: Chad introduces this live performance by telling the crowd the song Americans know as "Johnny Came Marching Home" originated from an Irish song called "Johnny I Hardly Knew Ye".  They then start performing "Johnny Comes Marching Home" and then start into "Johnny I Hardly Knew Ye" and then repeat this pattern. The songs share the same tune so they lend themselves well to a medley performance.
